### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 8080
@host = {{hostname}}:{{port}}
@post_id = 69654bccb9b2c974e8365a74

### Crear un nuevo post
POST http://{{host}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "title": "Mi primer post en Go",
    "content": "Este es el contenido del blog usando MongoDB v2",
    "author": "Tu Nombre"
}

### Obtener todos los posts
GET http://{{host}}/posts
Accept: application/json

### Obtener un post por ID
GET http://{{host}}/posts/{{post_id}}
Accept: application/json

###Obetener un post por nombre
GET http://{{host}}/posts?title=Mi%20primer%20post%20en%20Go
Accept: application/json

### Eliminar todos los posts
DELETE http://{{host}}/posts
Accept: application/json